Design Handoff — Integrations Feature
Overview
This document provides everything a frontend developer needs to implement the Integrations feature in StaffCo's web application (Quasar v2 / Vue 3) without a designer.
Resources:

Live prototype: [https://staffco-integrations.vercel.app/]
Prototype source code: https://github.com/parvinguseynov/integrations
PRD: [Link to Confluence — Unified.to Integration PRD]
Jira Stories: Story 9 (Integrations page), Story 10 (Task Settings), Story 11 (Messaging Settings)


The prototype is built in Next.js + React + shadcn/ui. You are implementing in Quasar v2 (Vue 3). Use the prototype as a pixel-perfect visual reference. Component mapping to Quasar is provided below.


